{"tid":1993164,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［機場特狗］班人一路睇一路屌 真係有啲無奈","createTime":"2020-04-28T14:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T15:35:13.000Z","uid":36716,"like":102,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7c7eb30fe47a6002042749858794f75190cdb5d5","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"老實講，真係希望大家唔好再睇機場特狗<br />\n<br />\n純屬個人意見：<br />\n其實我會明白.體諒亦理解d人仲用八達通，搭地鐵<br />\n甚至乎我都會去7-11買野飲，凌晨食m記<br />\n做到就做，儘量做，而唔強求其他人都一定要做<br />\n<br />\n甚至睇tvb咩愛回家 睇tvb新聞我都仲接受到，當然依幾樣我真係唔推薦<br />\n<br />\n但係唯獨<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場特狗</span></strong></span><br />\n依套真係擺到明係挑釁<br />\n唔止係維穩咁簡單<br />\n佢直情重用撐警藝人，完全唔將香港人放在眼內<br />\n真係好侮辱<br />\n<br />\n甚至佢依套野收得/多人討論，真係會對好多手足係心中都好負面<br />\n<br />\n依套野真係負面得好誇張<br />\n<br />\n所以我懇請大家真係唔好再睇<br />\n如果你仲自稱黃<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔介意你唔去集會 、搭地鐵 、睇愛回家、食海底撈<br />\n<br />\n但唯獨依套機場特狗，真係希望大家可以熄左屋企部電視</span>"},{"pid":"d923dc8626d00005efc81bb66e8c176548cc8a38","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"我希望你地能夠明白<br />\n<br />\n依套野唔止係維穩咁簡單<br />\n我真係覺得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果佢收得 係踐踏緊我尊嚴</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"066c5e5b348933e53c69c9e7fc3f815af68041f5","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"如果你屋企人睇而佢唔係藍（可能無咩立場既港豬）<br />\n<br />\n唯獨依一個鐘，搶左佢個電視權"},{"pid":"b192420d61d5bdf28e7cd962f5217edd90c26ad4","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"e3dce1ac83add71d21be7a20b9b05d5d2c35aaaa","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d923dc8626d00005efc81bb66e8c176548cc8a38","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"我希望你地能夠明白<br />\n<br />\n依套野唔止係維穩咁簡單<br />\n我真係覺得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果佢收得 係踐踏緊我尊嚴</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"我相信紅字唔止係我一個人既感受<br />\n<br />\n可能好多手足佢地既用詞真係會過火，令人難以接受<br />\n<br />\n但依套真係太離譜，真係放場運動係心既人真係會覺得好無奈"},{"pid":"a908bd2ee2be9b22b944f36834935537e0c81d5d","tid":1993164,"uid":19476,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1981162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1981162/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n依個垃圾post 呃到幾撚多正評 成班睇一樓就當真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e365571ce18faeb9decf5be0e902c238b29504","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:03:24.000Z","msg":"可能你地會覺得<br />\n<br />\n車，睇套劇姐，有無咁誇張<br />\n<br />\n但依套野由拍攝時間，主題，用人，都係諷刺緊場運動"},{"pid":"fae390b3844c4251025d1483cc465cf87ab2c8a7","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a908bd2ee2be9b22b944f36834935537e0c81d5d","tid":1993164,"uid":19476,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1981162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1981162/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n依個垃圾post 呃到幾撚多正評 成班睇一樓就當真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"係，佢地真係係入面討論<br />\n<br />\n令我自責既係<br />\n<br />\n依個po係由我帶起，我當時真係想屌<br />\n我想講：對唔住<br />\n<br />\n[推到完場］機場特警3<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1955256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1955256</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eea83550935b94f19d056b1caf20ef57b390c5cc","tid":1993164,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"希望更多人睇到"},{"pid":"9d0c089ec3ef7ef12ccba64be82dfa47e92530dd","tid":19